{"name":"Skinsplinter Plant","size":"large","type":"plant","tag":"","alignment":"chaotic evil","hitDice":"10","armorName":"natural armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":5,"otherArmorDesc":"17 (natural armor)","speed":"0","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"126 (12d10 + 60)","speedDesc":"30 ft., burrow 30 ft.","strPoints":"20","dexPoints":"8","conPoints":"20","intPoints":"5","wisPoints":"10","chaPoints":"5","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"90","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"4","customCr":"5 (1,800 XP)","customProf":3,"isLegendary":true,"legendariesDescription":"The [MON] can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The [MON] regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the earth elemental can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the earth elemental can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The earth elemental can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the earth elemental's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the earth elemental's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the earth elemental dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Blood Thirst","desc":"Upon dealing 113 damage, the skinsplinter vine will transform into a Skinsplinterer. The Skinsplinterer will have the [MON]'s current hp + 20."}],"actions":[{"name":"Summon Tendrils","desc":"The [MON] summons [1d4 + 2] thorned tendrils from the ground within 120ft.\nEach tendril has 6 hp and an AC of 9."},{"name":"Rake","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack_: [STR ATK] to hit, reach 15ft, one target.\n_Hit_: [STR 1d4] slashing damage."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[{"name":"Whirling Thorns","desc":"Each summoned tendril can make an Rake attack. Each successful hit restores [1d8] hit points to the [MON]."},{"name":"Lash","desc":"Two creatures within 30ft of the [MON] or a tendril must make a DC [STR SAVE] strength saving throw or be pulled 20ft towards the [MON]"},{"name":"Wall of Thorns","desc":"_1/day_: the [MON] can cast _Wall of Thorns_ as a 6th level spell, but cannot place the wall in a creature's space."}],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[],"damagetypes":[{"name":"bludgeoning","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"fire","note":" (Vulnerable)","type":"v"},{"name":"poison","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"psychic","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"}],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[{"name":"blinded"},{"name":"charmed"},{"name":"deafened"},{"name":"frightened"},{"name":"incapacitated"},{"name":"paralyzed"},{"name":"poisoned"},{"name":"prone"},{"name":"unconscious"}],"languages":[{"name":"Elvish","speaks":false}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":1,"damage":[]}